    "description": "電競歷史： 序章》是一款集时间管理、角色发展和深度迷你游戏于一体的 RPG 模拟器。你将扮演一名普通学生，将他培养成一名职业电竞选手。在比赛中击败老板，提高自己在社区中的声誉，成为最优秀的选手！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时间管理</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217120/extras/077fd375c5962d9ca869437795cf7294.poster.avif?t=1727355676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217120/extras/077fd375c5962d9ca869437795cf7294.webm?t=1727355676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>与最强玩家的竞赛从未停止。妥善管理训练和赚钱的时间，同时控制压力和疲劳，才能在战斗中脱颖而出。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >迷你游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217120/extras/cb5daa56aea5a9dd9578804bf7ec47c3.poster.avif?t=1727355676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217120/extras/cb5daa56aea5a9dd9578804bf7ec47c3.webm?t=1727355676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>享受过去热门游戏的另类版本。在电子竞技项目中发展：策略或射击。<br>在迷你游戏中，训练技能、升级技能树和精神状态都会影响角色的实力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造一个独特的角色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217120/extras/7e26a6e4a5cf13e317d0624d2f5095fa.poster.avif?t=1727355676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217120/extras/7e26a6e4a5cf13e317d0624d2f5095fa.webm?t=1727355676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>形成自己的游戏风格。随心所欲地升级你的特性和天赋。<br>是训练 AIM 以提高枪法，还是训练 Strafe 以变得难以捉摸？<br>是通过支配资源发展经济，还是通过微观控制取得胜利？一切由您决定。",
